      "text": "{user}さん\nまさか、そこにいないですよね？",
      "startTime": 25.7333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_sisiodoshi-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3233.333333400001,
          "startTime": 28.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenbath-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenbath-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……やっぱりか。すみません男湯はここしかなくて……\n壁越しに声が聞こえてしまって……",
      "startTime": 33.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_02-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、しょうがないですね\n今回くらいは許してあげますぅ～",
      "startTime": 42.5333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3400.0000000000055,
          "startTime": 41.1666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_sisiodoshi-01.m4a",
