      "text": "それは存在感がないってことでは……？",
      "startTime": 72.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_02-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、褒めてるんですよ",
      "startTime": 76.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_02-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "自分で言うのもなんですけど\n私達と仕事をするのって大変だと思うんです",
      "startTime": 82.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_02-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "それでも諦めずにマネジメントを続ける根性は\n素直に凄いと思いますよ",
      "startTime": 91.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_02-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "とはいえ、まだまだ至らないところだらけですけどね\nもう少し腕を上げてもらわないと困ります",
      "startTime": 99,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
